      "role": "user",
      "content": "but \"going against the status quo\" doesnt work for me because they just force me back into their version of reality. if i try to be myself, they use my \"needs\" as an excuse to control me even more. it's like i'm just a project to them, not a person. if everyone else is always pulling the strings, is there any way to actually make a choice that is truly, 100% mine? something they can't manipulate or take away?",
